# Postgres — local Docker by default. For Supabase, use the **Session pooler**
# URI from Dashboard → Connect (port 5432), not the direct db.*.supabase.co host
# (IPv6-only and often fails on home networks). On Vercel, transaction pooler
# (port 6543) also works with prepare: false in packages/db/src/client.ts.
DATABASE_URL=postgres://discover:discover@localhost:5432/discover
OPENAI_API_KEY=
